\n        CookieSpec browserCompatibilitySpec = CookiePolicy.getCookieSpec(\n                CookiePolicy.BROWSER_COMPATIBILITY);\n        CookieSpec netscapeSpec = CookiePolicy.getCookieSpec(CookiePolicy.NETSCAPE);\n        CookieSpec ignoreCookiesSpec = CookiePolicy.getCookieSpec(CookiePolicy.IGNORE_COOKIES);\n\n        assertThat(defaultSpec).isInstanceOf(RFC2109Spec.class);\n        assertThat(rfc2109Spec).isInstanceOf(RFC2109Spec.class);\n        assertThat(browserCompatibilitySpec).isInstanceOf(CookieSpecBase.class);\n        assertThat(netscapeSpec).isInstanceOf(NetscapeDraftSpec.class);\n        assertThat(ignoreCookiesSpec).isInstanceOf(IgnoreCookiesSpec.class);\n    }\n\n    private static CookiePolicyClassLoader newCookiePolicyClassLoader() {\n        URL location = CookiePolicy.class.getProtectionDomain().getCodeSource().getLocation();\n        return new CookiePolicyClassLoader(new URL[] {location},\n                CookiePolicyTest.class.getClassLoader());\n    }\n\n    private static final class CookiePolicyClassLoader extends URLClassLoader {\n        private CookiePolicyClassLoader(URL[] urls, ClassLoader parent) {\n            super(urls, parent);\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        protected Class<?> loadClass(String name, boolean resolve) throws ClassNotFoundException {\n            synchronized (getClassLoadingLock(name)) {\n                if (COOKIE_POLICY_CLASS_NAME.equals(name)) {\n                    Class<?> loadedClass = findLoadedClass(name);\n                    if (loadedClass == null) {\n                        loadedClass = findClass(name);\n                    }\n                    if (resolve) {\n                        resolveClass(loadedClass);\n                    }\n                    return loadedClass;\n                }\n                return super.loadClass(name, resolve);\n            }\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1778675287091}}
[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Refining classloader issues**\n\nI need to refine my understanding of the classloader processes. It seems like the fresh classloader might not cover everything needed due to potential initialization issues in the JVM. Maybe the agent doesn’t see certain things because of tests catching errors. I’m wondering if there are aspects of dynamic class loading that are unsupported. Also, I need to analyze how imports and static references impact the initialization of classes like CookiePolicy. There’s a lack of clarity about order in testing, too.\n\n**Investigating CookiePolicy initialization**\n\nI’m trying to understand how the initialization of CookiePolicy works with the classloader. If registeredCookieSpecsCanBeInstantiatedByPolicy runs first, does that mean CookiePolicy is initialized by the system loader? Yet, the fresh classloader should create its own copy unless it delegates dependencies. It seems like Class.forName uses the caller's class loader, which complicates things. There might be factors like whether the agent excludes classes loaded in a custom loader or if NativeImageSupport affects it. I wonder if jacoco measures coverage based on specific source lines, and whether dynamic access call sites need instrumentation.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_01aa693fe8b2a591016a046e481bac819f815b95ff9f71a78d\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqBG5WVJdhcFQ4r0j3iiuI2_g-mVcl75WdpXoizfFojul2BlYx0J10zpHs6zUFTfzzBYyJv7R35vIfB3FTUyuEElbM3T-iBWQXpqK6SgVrLRHoaVm_sIuDDIkC6k9uz99ZCd6fi244Rxoilmy8ccmzZ5k3_164KHA6kwavkEn35oRlIIHKfPS8Lk5WZZtNmZavGjihFT7Nt_dCcmHK0ytr3dV-QDJWnl4_4sFFQlcAumN0JonUG8KT4N9Bbfiu2CzHiuSQny2H0IlqzTS579YxWrJAP2-qRBq3qyBBDDHLJetRCXFiWrGECj61EnepCelsrnlXeBGSdyt4XWbHbN-WsQ-15jYu6RZ2NH24EhzsTlAefmmlchgi-rcqbJlJmJzCVKrBm3m_kWWGK8JuAcNlZOqoNlnFdnsN9m5q9ol2x5sUVveOZXnuR5NrEknXllEVU14jgjHWgPc9wl4dg_i8irrNcotUqJuro8ZhBjOm-jGnlr6dFSZi